&lt;h3>Available helpers&lt;span class="hx-absolute -hx-mt-20" id="available-helpers">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#available-helpers" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h3>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;code>composeBeforeSend(...fns)&lt;/code> – combine multiple &lt;code>beforeSend&lt;/code> functions&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>composePostTest(...fns)&lt;/code> – combine multiple &lt;code>postTest&lt;/code> functions&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>delay(tests, ms)&lt;/code> – add a delay before each case runs&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>focus(tests)&lt;/code> – mark tests as focused&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>repeat(tests, count)&lt;/code> – run tests sequentially multiple times&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>bombard(tests, count)&lt;/code> – launch multiple concurrent runs&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>skip(tests)&lt;/code> – skip the provided cases&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>setup(tests)&lt;/code> – mark tests with &lt;code>phase: 'setup'&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>teardown(tests)&lt;/code> – mark tests with &lt;code>phase: 'teardown'&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>recording(tests, mode)&lt;/code> – override the HTTP recording mode (&lt;code>off&lt;/code>, &lt;code>replay&lt;/code>, or &lt;code>record&lt;/code>) for the provided cases&lt;/li>
